Module-level tap wildcards (e.g., ~tap(mymodule:* -> *))

Currently we support:
- Universal wildcards: ~tap(* -> *)
- Meta event wildcards: ~tap(koru:* -> *)

Need to add:
- Module-specific wildcards: ~tap(mymodule:* -> *)

This enables targeted profiling/logging of all events in a specific module
without intercepting the entire program.

Implementation likely in taps.kz pattern matching logic.
